<p>In my case, I need use comments for debug purposes, prior the output of the JSON structure. So I decided to use debug information in the HTTP header, to avoid breaking the client:</p>

<pre><code>header("My-Json-Comment: Yes, I know it's a workaround ;-) ");
</code></pre>

